Trip Tracker About & FAQ text

Trip Tracker is an app for the modern traveler, the person who plans their trip through a series of emails, phone-memos, to-do lists, and post-it notes.
We've built a platform to help you keep everything in one place, easily accessible, and easy to update.
From your flight info to your packing list, Trip Tracker will help you stay organized and eliminate the dreaded feeling of leaving behind something important.
